quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,31,aur jo tum mein se khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmanbardar rahay gi aur amal naik kere gi. is ko hum dona sawab den ge aur is ke liye hum ne izzat ki rozi tayyar kar rakhi hai
  33,32,ae paighambar ki byoyo tum aur aurton ki terhan nahi ho. agar tum parhaizgaar rehna chahti ho to kisi ( ajnabi shakhs se ) naram naram baatein nahkiya karo taakay woh shakhs jis ke dil mein kisi terhan ka marz hai koi umeed ( nah ) peda kere. aur un dastoor ke mutabiq baatkiya karo
  33,33,aur apne gharon mein thahri raho aur jis terhan ( pehlay ) jahliat ( ke dinon ) mein izhaar Tajammal karti theen is terhan zeenat nah dikhao. aur namaz padti raho aur zakaat deti raho aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karti raho. ae ( paighambar ke ) ahal beeet khuda chahta hai ke tum se napaaki ( ka mil kuchail ) daur kardey aur tumhe bilkul pak saaf kardey
  33,34,aur tumahray gharon mein jo khuda ki ayatain parhi jati hain aur hikmat ( ki baatein sunai jati hain ) un ko yaad rakho. be shak khuda bareek been aur bakhabar hai
  33,35,( jo log khuda ke agay sir itaat khham karne walay hain yani ) musalman mard aur musalman aurtain aur momin mard aur momin aurtain aur farmaa bardaar mard aur farmaa bardaar aurtain aur raast baz mard aur raast baz aurtain aur sabr karne walay mard aur sabr karne wali aurtain aur farotni karne walay mard aur farotni karne wali aurtain aur khairaat karne walay mard aur aur khairaat karne wali aurtain aur rozay rakhnay walay mard aur rozay rakhnay wali aurtain aur apni sharamgahon ki hifazat karne walay mard aur hifazat karne wali aurtain aur khuda ko kasrat se yaad karne walay mard aur kasrat se yaad karne wali aurtain. kuch shak nahi ke un ke liye khuda ne bakhshish aur ajar azeem tayyar kar rakha hai
